// FALLING PETALS for(let i=0;i<30;i++){ let petal=document.createElement("div"); petal.className="petal"; petal.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw"; petal.style.animationDuration=(5+Math.random()*5)+"s"; petal.style.opacity=Math.random(); document.body.appendChild(petal); } // COUNTDOWN TO VALENTINE (Philadelphia time) function updateCountdown(){ const now = new Date(new Date().toLocaleString("en-US",{timeZone:"America/New_York"})); const valentines = new Date("Feb 14, 2026 00:00:00"); const diff = valentines - now; const d = Math.floor(diff/(1000*60*60*24)); const h = Math.floor((diff/(1000*60*60))%24); const m = Math.floor((diff/(1000*60))%60); const s = Math.floor((diff/1000)%60); document.getElementById("countdown").innerHTML = `Countdown to Valentine‚Äôs Day (your time ‚ù§Ô∏è): ${d}d ${h}h ${m}m ${s}s`; } setInterval(updateCountdown,1000);
